      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**管线新鲜度**（`quant-feature-bus` 每 ~30s）：`ticks_1m`/`bars_1m`/`bus_bars_1min` &lt;5min；`features_120T` &lt;20min；`features_240T` &lt;4.5h；`macro_seed` &lt;48h。**磁盘** &gt;80% 删旧日志；ticks/bars 只删确认过期月份。目录 `du` 约 5min 刷新。若整行 No data：查 Prometheus Targets `quant-feature-bus:9192` 是否 UP。"
